data.description: Looking for beautiful land? Look no further! This beautiful 5.7 ACRES is located in a prime location.  Property located 1 mile from Kickapoo turnpike. Long driveway located off Reno providing great privacy off main road.  Additional entry to acreage located off of Yoachum.  This beautiful property is in a wonderful location to build your dream home, run cattle, or have horses.  The possibilities are endless.  Schedule your showing today!
